{"parentUuid":"3302b999-904e-4b45-8f3e-029cbd48105a","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/kokiyoshida/Knowhere-inc/baseball_detector_api","sessionId":"8204bdf6-de36-4c8e-9d59-138ba27c95d5","version":"2.0.1","gitBranch":"feat/add-item-group-api","message":{"id":"msg_01VNf381gKnGLqGdcbwxoQcs","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GET /subscription-groups は以下のレスポンスを返します：\n\n```typescript\n{\n  subscriptionGroups: SubscriptionGroup[],\n  total: number\n}\n```\n\n**SubscriptionGroup の構造：**\n\n- `id`: string (UUID)\n- `stripePriceTableId`: string | null\n- `appleSubscriptionGroupId`: number | null\n- `isActive`: boolean\n- `teamType`: string (例: 'single', 'multiple')\n- `createdAt`: Date\n- `updatedAt`: Date\n- `subscriptions`: Subscription[] (リレーション)\n\n**取得条件：**\n\n- `isActive: true`\n- `teamType: 'single'`\n- サブスクリプションに `isSubscription: true` のアイテムを含む\n\n**リレーション：**\n\n各 `SubscriptionGroup` には `subscriptions` 配列が含まれ、その中には：\n- `items`: サブスクリプションアイテム\n  - `aiCoachs`: AI コーチ情報\n  - `balls`: ボール情報\n\n`createdAt` の昇順でソートされ、`total` には配列の要素数が設定されます。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1030,"cache_read_input_tokens":27911,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1030,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":312,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CTehWEMktXst8gHkTekfo","type":"assistant","uuid":"6382c7cd-cc30-4075-b714-aa758954cc3e","timestamp":"2025-09-30T13:55:09.077Z"}
